# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../timeline.rst:23
msgid "Timeline"
msgstr "Vremenska Crta"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../timeline.rst:25
msgid ""
"The timeline is where your video comes together. You arrange clips, trim "
"them, layer visuals, and make timing decisions here. If you are new to "
"editing, think of the timeline as a simple left-to-right story: earlier "
"moments on the left, later moments on the right."
msgstr ""
"Vremenska crta je mjesto gdje se vaš video sastavlja. Ovdje raspoređujete "
"isječke, skraćujete ih, slagate vizuale u slojeve i donosite odluke o "
"vremenu. Ako ste novi u uređivanju, zamislite vremensku crtu kao jednostavnu "
"priču s lijeva na desno: raniji trenuci s lijeve strane, kasniji trenuci s "
"desne strane."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../timeline.rst:32
msgid ""
"If you are just getting started, read :ref:`quick_tutorial_ref` first, then "
"come back here for more detail. For a labeled breakdown of toolbar controls, "
"see :ref:`timeline_toolbar_ref`."
msgstr ""
"Ako tek počinjete, prvo pročitajte :ref:`quick_tutorial_ref`, a zatim se "
"vratite ovdje za više detalja. Za označeni pregled kontrola alatne trake, "
"pogledajte :ref:`timeline_toolbar_ref`."

