"centriranje i zumiranje)."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../timeline.rst:91
msgid ""
"Tip: If timeline editing feels crowded, zoom in with the timeline slider to "
"make small clip adjustments easier."
msgstr ""
"Savjet: Ako uređivanje vremenske crte djeluje zbijeno, povećajte zum pomoću "
"klizača vremenske crte kako biste olakšali male prilagodbe isječaka."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../timeline.rst:94
msgid ""
"You can also zoom the timeline with :kbd:`Ctrl+Scroll Wheel`. On the QWidget "
"timeline, hold :kbd:`Ctrl` and drag with the middle mouse button for smooth "
"zooming."
msgstr ""
"Također možete zumirati vremensku crtu pomoću :kbd:`Ctrl+Scroll Wheel`. Na "
"QWidget vremenskoj crti, držite :kbd:`Ctrl` i povucite srednjim gumbom miša "
"za glatko zumiranje."

